{"tid":555918,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本藝術家畫「台灣加油」　旋轉90度超驚喜","createTime":"2018-02-10T03:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T04:05:28.000Z","uid":72478,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6319c13da943e77b551cf836ec17ed3f6e85f98f","tid":555918,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T03:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3111/d3111206.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3111%2Fd3111206.jpg&h=71b98c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本藝術家畫「台灣加油」，替花蓮地震所有的受難民眾打氣。（圖／翻攝自野村一晟推特）<br />\n<br />\n花蓮6日晚上11時50分發生規模6.0地震，目前已知12人死亡、279人輕重傷、仍有5人失聯，各國媒體也紛紛報導關注。日本一名高中美術科教師、藝術家野村一晟，聽聞台灣花蓮發生地震之後，就用自己擅長的「雙向圖」畫了一副「台灣加油！」替台灣災民祈福。<br />\n<br />\n藝術家野村一晟非常擅長雙向圖，日前就設計過把「挑戰」變「勝利」、「最強」變「戰場」等畫，這次他則在Twitter上以拍攝影片的方式，用紅色顏料畫出「台灣」漢字，接著轉動90度後，「台灣」立刻變成「加油」，透過用心的作品表達對台灣的關心。<br />\n<br />\n許多台灣網友看了紛紛留言說：「謝謝你，我們是一家人。」、「謝謝野村先生！」、「謝謝野村一晟先生及各位對台灣的關心，身為台灣的一份子，我覺得非常感動！！」、「就像魔術一樣&hellip;&hellip;驚人的藝術家。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藝術家Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/IsseiNomura\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIsseiNomura&d=h3oADuDJK3jSendkQNSAcaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=69d963dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/IsseiNomura</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180210/1111741.htm#ixzz56foOTEDr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180210%2F1111741.htm%23ixzz56foOTEDr&d=h3oADuDJK3jSendkQNSAcaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=8102bf3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180210/1111741.htm#ixzz56foOTEDr</a>"},{"pid":"d286f297cd68f8b6a218a4a40204a4c5bcb2c1cc","tid":555918,"uid":20890,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"班台狗見到仲唔高潮？"},{"pid":"122b57f7f15b28d9484e4a463600636c61d3b9db","tid":555918,"uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20